title: How long is Caitlyn gonna take Riot?
body: I wanted to practice my Caitlyn for ranked this weekend and haven't been able to. How long is this bug fix gonna take? It's been like 5 days now.

replies.body: She wont be back until all the Caitlyn Jenner stuff dies down on the net so they can release the Caitlyn Jenner Skin
I know the feels, when it happened to viktor.
If you want to practice caitlyn pick a spot on your desktop and right click it repeatedly
hi, cait is just a rude champion to play because she outranges everyone and makes them feel sorrow and grief.
